I made this dish a few times and WOW. Its very delicious...However...I made a few changes before I was satisfied with it. The major change is that I cut and marinate the chicken breasts in lemon juice and a small spoon of Dijon mustard before I cooke it, you would not believe how much difference this makes. I also added a lot more garlic and instead of whipping cream I used heavy whipping cream (you can get it from the same place as the whipping cream). Finally, I found that using something besides regular fettuccine, like herb fettuccine adds extra flavor and works great. THIS IS A WINNER, you just have to be a bit creative with it. =)

