We make this dish in Little Italy too. Here's how to improve it. Use 6 lg. breast instead, cook for 7 min w/ 2 tbsp butter. Use 2 minced shallot and saute. Add 1 tsp red pepper w/garlic, saute 5 min. Simmer stock and 2 cups cream for 10-12 min. Use 12 oz.'s fettucine. Sauce is a compliment. Never overwhelm the PASTA.

